 Proto was bored out of his mind. He need a name. He thought about it. How 
about joesph stalen. Yea thats good. Joesph Stalen is the fiddler on the 
roof. Joseph Stalin is on Broadway. He scratched his head and decided 
against. It sounded a little to much like a human name. Russian even. He 
would have to think further.
